text: Oktyabrsky () is a rural locality (a village) in Nadezhdinsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 100 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 49 km from Iglino, 2 km from Pyatiletka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Oktyabrsky, Iglinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
